data.description: Beautiful Corner Lot Home In Well Established Neighborhood. 3 Bedrooms, 2 Baths With Updated Colors, Appliances, Windows And Beautiful Hardwood Floors. Bonus Room Over Garage, Large 16X12 Detached Storage Building And Fenced in Yard. Updated bathroom with Jacuzzi Tub. Walking Distance to Elementary, Middle and High Schools. Super Convenient To Shopping And Entertainment. Great Neighbors, Move in Ready.
